data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Home located in highly sought after community of Basset Creek at K-Bar Ranch features 2848 sq ft of living space, 4 bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths, plus bonus room, den/office & extra deep 2 car garage.  The charming tree-lined street brings you to the home that backs onto a pond.  As you enter the home the open floorplan is great for your living needs and entertaining.  There is an office/den with double doors off the foyer.  The formal dining room opens into the spacious family room.  The heart of the home is the kitchen with an abundance of cabinets and counter space, island, granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances.  There is a powder room downstairs as well as the laundry room.  Upstairs the relaxing primary bedroom has a large walk-in closet.  The primary bathroom has double sinks, granite countertops, a garden tub and separate shower. There are 3 spacious bedrooms as well as a second bathroom with double sinks, granite countertops and tub/shower combination.  The large bonus room perfect for a movie or game night completes the living areas upstairs.  Enjoy the Florida living on your large screened and covered lanai and fully fenced backyard overlooking a pond.   The neighborhood features a Community center with tennis court, basketball court, playground and pool. Close to schools, I-75/275, Tampa International Airport & downtown Tampa, MacDill AFB, hospitals, shopping, outlet mall, schools, golf courses, restaurants. This home is a Must See & will not last!!!
